5
00:00:08,570 --> 00:00:11,070
<font color="yellow">You can't go through those without my permission.</font>

6
00:00:11,300 --> 00:00:12,440
<font color="yellow">Sorry.</font>

7
00:00:13,270 --> 00:00:14,740
<font color="yellow">Hold on.</font>

8
00:00:15,870 --> 00:00:20,770
<font color="yellow">I want to ask you something, just in case.</font>

9
00:00:21,040 --> 00:00:23,500
<font color="yellow">I'm just worried, that's all.</font>

10
00:00:25,640 --> 00:00:29,640
<font color="yellow">I know this is ridiculous, but I'm just asking.</font>

11
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:32,240
<font color="yellow">By any chance,</font>

12
00:00:32,970 --> 00:00:34,770
<font color="yellow">do you...</font>

13
00:00:35,070 --> 00:00:36,570
<font color="yellow">happen to like me?</font>

14
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:43,700
<font color="yellow">- Oh, no. - I don't believe this.</font>

15
00:00:44,170 --> 00:00:48,100
<font color="yellow">How could you say something like that so brazenly?</font>

16
00:00:48,340 --> 00:00:50,570
<font color="yellow">How can you say that so nonchalantly?</font>

17
00:00:51,300 --> 00:00:54,470
<font color="yellow">I don't know. I think I lost my mind for a few seconds.</font>

18
00:00:54,670 --> 00:00:56,740
<font color="yellow">Pretend you didn't hear that.</font>

19
00:00:56,840 --> 00:00:59,870
<font color="yellow">How can I do that when I heard it so clearly?</font>

20
00:01:00,740 --> 00:01:03,140
<font color="yellow">Is something wrong with you?</font>

21
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:05,470
<font color="yellow">I think so. You might be right.</font>

22
00:01:06,300 --> 00:01:09,370
<font color="yellow">I think I lost my mind for a while.</font>

23
00:01:09,570 --> 00:01:13,800
<font color="yellow">I didn't ask because I had an ulterior motive.</font>

24
00:01:14,500 --> 00:01:17,870
<font color="yellow">I just saw that you'd taken a whole load of photos of me.</font>

25
00:01:18,110 --> 00:01:19,140
<font color="yellow">I was just curious.</font>

26
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:22,240
<font color="yellow">I know I was wrong, but I wanted to be sure.</font>

27
00:01:22,870 --> 00:01:24,240
<font color="yellow">I'm really sorry.</font>

28
00:01:25,670 --> 00:01:27,740
<font color="yellow">Were you very surprised?</font>

29
00:01:28,170 --> 00:01:32,700
<font color="yellow">If I were you in your shoes, I would have been taken aback, too.</font>

30
00:01:32,940 --> 00:01:37,270
<font color="yellow">Like I told you earlier, I didn't get much sleep last night.</font>

31
00:01:37,500 --> 00:01:41,240
<font color="yellow">I think that caused my brain to go a bit haywire.</font>

32
00:01:41,440 --> 00:01:43,200
<font color="yellow">If I don't get enough sleep,</font>

33
00:01:43,600 --> 00:01:46,200
<font color="yellow">everything in my head gets jumbled up,</font>

34
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:49,570
<font color="yellow">and I can't do anything properly the next day.</font>

35
00:01:49,570 --> 00:01:51,170
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

36
00:01:52,470 --> 00:01:55,640
<font color="yellow">Shall I get you a cold drink to help you cool off?</font>

37
00:01:55,740 --> 00:01:58,140
<font color="yellow">No, it's fine.</font>

38
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:01,670
<font color="yellow">No, leave it. I'll clean it up.</font>

39
00:02:01,770 --> 00:02:02,800
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

40
00:02:05,470 --> 00:02:07,800
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with me?</font>

41
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:10,570
<font color="yellow">Why did I say such a thing?</font>

42
00:02:12,870 --> 00:02:15,840
<font color="yellow">How am I supposed to face him from now on?</font>

43
00:02:20,170 --> 00:02:22,800
<font color="yellow">How can she say something like that so directly?</font>

44
00:02:23,510 --> 00:02:25,370
<font color="yellow">She's unbelievable.</font>

45
00:03:20,570 --> 00:03:22,040
<font color="yellow">Why did I do that?</font>

46
00:03:22,370 --> 00:03:24,140
<font color="yellow">Do I really...</font>

47
00:03:26,900 --> 00:03:28,670
<font color="yellow">No, it can't be.</font>

48
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:40,200
<font color="yellow">Walking down this street with you feels like a dream.</font>

49
00:03:40,300 --> 00:03:41,540
<font color="yellow">It does.</font>

50
00:03:42,100 --> 00:03:44,870
<font color="yellow">Walking down this street with you...</font>

51
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:48,340
<font color="yellow">makes me feel like we went back in time.</font>

52
00:03:49,140 --> 00:03:51,470
<font color="yellow">You can't leave us ever again.</font>

53
00:03:51,670 --> 00:03:54,070
<font color="yellow">Stay with us forever.</font>

54
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:57,970
<font color="yellow">Will you look who's here?</font>

55
00:03:58,170 --> 00:03:59,800
<font color="yellow">Mr Lee, you're back.</font>

56
00:03:59,900 --> 00:04:02,000
<font color="yellow">Hello. How have you been?</font>

57
00:04:02,270 --> 00:04:04,770
<font color="yellow">Where were you all this time?</font>

58
00:04:05,100 --> 00:04:08,670
<font color="yellow">The whole neighbourhood felt empty because you were gone.</font>

59
00:04:08,770 --> 00:04:11,370
<font color="yellow">I had some business to take care of.</font>

60
00:04:11,370 --> 00:04:13,770
<font color="yellow">Mr Lee.</font>

61
00:04:13,770 --> 00:04:16,810
<font color="yellow">I was so afraid I wouldn't get to see you before I died.</font>

62
00:04:16,810 --> 00:04:18,340
<font color="yellow">I'm glad you're back.</font>

63
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:20,270
<font color="yellow">You've gotten even younger.</font>

64
00:04:20,270 --> 00:04:21,640
<font color="yellow">- Don't say that. - Thanks.</font>

65
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:23,140
<font color="yellow">- Mr Lee! - Are you well?</font>

66
00:04:23,140 --> 00:04:24,340
<font color="yellow">Yes, I am.</font>

67
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:26,970
<font color="yellow">Hello, Seul Gi. It's been a while.</font>

68
00:04:26,970 --> 00:04:29,770
<font color="yellow">Seul Gi recognised you from far away and wanted to say hi.</font>

69
00:04:29,770 --> 00:04:31,470
<font color="yellow">It really is you.</font>

70
00:04:31,470 --> 00:04:34,540
<font color="yellow">Did you miss me that much?</font>

71
00:04:36,500 --> 00:04:39,940
<font color="yellow">You have no idea how badly she wanted to see you.</font>

72
00:04:39,940 --> 00:04:43,000
<font color="yellow">- Will you come by every day? - Yes.</font>

73
00:04:43,640 --> 00:04:45,240
<font color="yellow">- Were you sick? - Welcome back.</font>

74
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,940
<font color="yellow">- Visit us often. - Sure.</font>

75
00:04:48,670 --> 00:04:50,200
<font color="yellow">Mr Lee's back.</font>

76
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:53,840
<font color="yellow">Mr Lee.</font>

77
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:56,640
<font color="yellow">It's been a while. Are you well?</font>

78
00:04:56,740 --> 00:05:00,670
<font color="yellow">Yes. Yun Shil told me that you had come back.</font>

79
00:05:00,670 --> 00:05:03,340
<font color="yellow">You have no idea how pleased I was. Welcome back.</font>

80
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:06,940
<font color="yellow">Thank you for taking care of my shop for me.</font>

81
00:05:23,870 --> 00:05:27,240
<font color="yellow">(Lee Man Sool)</font>

82
00:05:39,170 --> 00:05:40,870
<font color="yellow">It's just the same.</font>

83
00:05:41,370 --> 00:05:43,000
<font color="yellow">Nothing has changed.</font>

84
00:05:44,270 --> 00:05:45,440
<font color="yellow">Of course not.</font>

85
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:48,470
<font color="yellow">The store belongs to you.</font>

86
00:05:48,470 --> 00:05:52,770
<font color="yellow">No. Wolgyesu Tailor Shop belongs to you all now.</font>

87
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,470
<font color="yellow">It's not mine any more.</font>

88
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:57,370
<font color="yellow">What do you mean, Sir?</font>

89
00:05:57,470 --> 00:06:00,770
<font color="yellow">New wine should be kept in new wine skins.</font>

90
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:04,600
<font color="yellow">Old people like me should step aside in due time.</font>

91
00:06:05,170 --> 00:06:09,440
<font color="yellow">Just like how I inherited this store from my father,</font>

92
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:12,500
<font color="yellow">I now found people I trust to take over.</font>

93
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:15,740
<font color="yellow">I can now retire with a happy heart.</font>

94
00:06:15,940 --> 00:06:17,670
<font color="yellow">I can't let you do that.</font>

95
00:06:17,970 --> 00:06:21,040
<font color="yellow">I can't handle this store without your help.</font>

96
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,970
<font color="yellow">I have a lot to learn.</font>

97
00:06:23,140 --> 00:06:24,940
<font color="yellow">You can't retire yet.</font>

98
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:29,340
<font color="yellow">You proved your skill and worth at the competition.</font>

99
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:31,340
<font color="yellow">Now that I'm old,</font>

100
00:06:32,170 --> 00:06:35,100
<font color="yellow">my eyes are dim and my hands are clumsy.</font>

101
00:06:35,370 --> 00:06:37,470
<font color="yellow">They even shake sometimes.</font>

102
00:06:40,870 --> 00:06:41,900
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

103
00:06:42,140 --> 00:06:43,170
<font color="yellow">Listen.</font>

104
00:06:44,870 --> 00:06:49,700
<font color="yellow">With your skill, you and Dong Jin can manage this store just fine.</font>

105
00:06:49,900 --> 00:06:55,670
<font color="yellow">You have Ms Geum to rely on, and you also have Yun Shil.</font>

106
00:07:05,470 --> 00:07:06,700
<font color="yellow">Dong Sook, wait.</font>

107
00:07:08,270 --> 00:07:10,270
<font color="yellow">I couldn't sleep a wink last night.</font>

108
00:07:10,370 --> 00:07:11,400
<font color="yellow">Why not?</font>

109
00:07:16,100 --> 00:07:18,470
<font color="yellow">I knew you'd regret it.</font>

110
00:07:18,700 --> 00:07:22,270
<font color="yellow">I told you not to buy it, but you said you only live once.</font>

111
00:07:22,570 --> 00:07:24,300
<font color="yellow">Now did you get your senses back?</font>

112
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:27,000
<font color="yellow">I wasn't in my right mind yesterday.</font>

113
00:07:27,300 --> 00:07:29,840
<font color="yellow">Can I go back and ask for a refund?</font>

114
00:07:29,940 --> 00:07:31,070
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

115
00:07:31,370 --> 00:07:35,140
<font color="yellow">You took it with you to a restaurant and a club.</font>

116
00:07:35,340 --> 00:07:38,540
<font color="yellow">- You can't ask for a refund. - No, right?</font>

117
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:39,870
<font color="yellow">That's just wrong.</font>

118
00:07:39,970 --> 00:07:42,370
<font color="yellow">Can you buy this bag off me?</font>

119
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:44,400
<font color="yellow">I'll give you a 30-percent discount.</font>

120
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:48,200
<font color="yellow">I can't afford to buy an expensive handbag like that.</font>

121
00:07:48,300 --> 00:07:51,340
<font color="yellow">I'm even thinking about selling the handbags I already have.</font>

122
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:52,570
<font color="yellow">You're right.</font>

123
00:07:54,740 --> 00:07:56,640
<font color="yellow">I'm already short of money this month.</font>

124
00:07:57,000 --> 00:08:01,170
<font color="yellow">I spent all the money we had saved up before we moved here.</font>

125
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,370
<font color="yellow">I might end up penniless at this rate.</font>

126
00:08:05,540 --> 00:08:07,170
<font color="yellow">Good morning, Dong Sook.</font>

127
00:08:07,470 --> 00:08:09,000
<font color="yellow">What are you doing here?</font>

128
00:08:09,570 --> 00:08:12,100
<font color="yellow">I brought you this. One of my tenants...</font>

129
00:08:12,500 --> 00:08:15,770
<font color="yellow">gave me a box of crabs, saying her parents sent them.</font>

130
00:08:15,970 --> 00:08:18,540
<font color="yellow">I brought them to give to your mother.</font>

131
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:23,300
<font color="yellow">You could eat them yourself. Gifts make me feel uncomfortable.</font>

132
00:08:23,300 --> 00:08:27,140
<font color="yellow">Don't say things like that. That hurts me a lot, you know.</font>

133
00:08:30,070 --> 00:08:31,440
<font color="yellow">Yes, Dong Sook.</font>

134
00:08:31,740 --> 00:08:36,270
<font color="yellow">He brought them for you. Thank him and say you'll enjoy them.</font>

135
00:08:38,500 --> 00:08:41,570
<font color="yellow">I don't want to, but thanks.</font>

136
00:08:42,540 --> 00:08:45,600
<font color="yellow">It's heavy. I'll take it inside and greet your mother, as well.</font>

137
00:08:45,700 --> 00:08:48,300
<font color="yellow">She went to the sauna. I'll take it.</font>

138
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:49,500
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

139
00:08:56,470 --> 00:08:58,040
<font color="yellow">Crabs are all good,</font>

140
00:08:58,410 --> 00:09:01,870
<font color="yellow">but do you know what Dong Sook likes the most in the whole world?</font>

141
00:09:03,340 --> 00:09:06,910
<font color="yellow">What Dong Sook likes the most in the whole world?</font>

142
00:09:07,670 --> 00:09:09,700
<font color="yellow">That's me, Park Dae Sub.</font>

143
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:16,240
<font color="yellow">My goodness. You're such a funny man.</font>

144
00:09:18,170 --> 00:09:21,410
<font color="yellow">The thing Dong Sook likes the most in the whole world...</font>

145
00:09:21,940 --> 00:09:24,500
<font color="yellow">are expensive handbags like this.</font>

146
00:09:25,970 --> 00:09:27,740
<font color="yellow">- Expensive handbags? - Dong Sook...</font>

147
00:09:27,740 --> 00:09:29,870
<font color="yellow">wanted this handbag so much.</font>

148
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:34,070
<font color="yellow">You'd earn a lot of brownie points if you bought it for her.</font>

149
00:09:34,300 --> 00:09:36,300
<font color="yellow">Dong Sook, get over here quick.</font>

150
00:09:36,300 --> 00:09:37,640
<font color="yellow">- What? - Come here.</font>

151
00:09:38,140 --> 00:09:39,740
<font color="yellow">Do you want this?</font>

152
00:09:41,870 --> 00:09:43,070
<font color="yellow">Sun Nyeo.</font>

153
00:09:44,300 --> 00:09:46,140
<font color="yellow">This is unbelievable.</font>

154
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:47,910
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

155
00:09:48,670 --> 00:09:51,770
<font color="yellow">If you want to buy it, I'll give you a 20-percent discount.</font>

156
00:09:51,770 --> 00:09:53,270
<font color="yellow">It's yours for 1,600 dollars.</font>

157
00:09:53,470 --> 00:09:54,840
<font color="yellow">1,600 dollars?</font>

158
00:09:56,570 --> 00:09:57,570
<font color="yellow">1,600?</font>

159
00:09:59,640 --> 00:10:00,740
<font color="yellow">Let's do this.</font>

160
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:04,040
<font color="yellow">There's a building in Yeongdeungpo that I've been eyeing.</font>

161
00:10:04,140 --> 00:10:07,100
<font color="yellow">Once I buy that building, I'll buy this for you.</font>

162
00:10:07,100 --> 00:10:10,000
<font color="yellow">- Wait until then, Dong Sook. - You're so cheap.</font>

163
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:13,370
<font color="yellow">Bags don't cost a fortune. Why wait until you buy a building?</font>

164
00:10:13,570 --> 00:10:17,140
<font color="yellow">I save up dimes and quarters to make a dollar.</font>

165
00:10:17,670 --> 00:10:20,140
<font color="yellow">That's how hard I saved up to become a landlord.</font>

166
00:10:20,340 --> 00:10:22,340
<font color="yellow">Not that story again.</font>

167
00:10:22,740 --> 00:10:23,970
<font color="yellow">I'm going upstairs.</font>

168
00:10:24,300 --> 00:10:25,340
<font color="yellow">Why...</font>

169
00:10:27,570 --> 00:10:28,600
<font color="yellow">Dong Sook.</font>

170
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:31,800
<font color="yellow">Can you spare me some time this evening?</font>

171
00:10:32,040 --> 00:10:34,970
<font color="yellow">- What for? - To show you my buildings.</font>

172
00:10:35,340 --> 00:10:38,170
<font color="yellow">Once you see the buildings I own,</font>

173
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:41,070
<font color="yellow">you won't even want a truckload of those handbags.</font>

174
00:10:51,740 --> 00:10:54,700
<font color="yellow">What's... What's that you're hugging?</font>

175
00:10:57,340 --> 00:11:00,040
<font color="yellow">It's a handbag that Dong Sook wants.</font>

176
00:11:00,370 --> 00:11:02,170
<font color="yellow">If you want to buy it,</font>

177
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:05,440
<font color="yellow">I'll give you a special 20-percent...</font>

178
00:11:06,170 --> 00:11:08,000
<font color="yellow">I know how strapped you are.</font>

179
00:11:08,500 --> 00:11:10,870
<font color="yellow">I'll give you 40 percent off the retail price.</font>

180
00:11:11,170 --> 00:11:14,600
<font color="yellow">Is this the handbag that Dong Sook wants?</font>

181
00:11:14,740 --> 00:11:15,840
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

182
00:11:16,100 --> 00:11:20,470
<font color="yellow">If you give this to her, you'll earn a load of brownie points.</font>

183
00:11:20,740 --> 00:11:24,440
<font color="yellow">The day you give this to Dong Sook,</font>

184
00:11:25,070 --> 00:11:27,970
<font color="yellow">Mr Park will be thrown out of the picture.</font>

185
00:11:32,540 --> 00:11:33,940
<font color="yellow">- Keep it for me. - What?</font>

186
00:11:33,940 --> 00:11:37,100
<font color="yellow">I'll buy it off you when I make a hit album.</font>

187
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,740
<font color="yellow">I shouldn't have asked.</font>

188
00:11:38,940 --> 00:11:41,840
<font color="yellow">Don't sell it to anyone else. I'll buy it off you.</font>

189
00:11:45,470 --> 00:11:46,970
<font color="yellow">When will that be?</font>

190
00:11:50,170 --> 00:11:52,170
<font color="yellow">What should I do with you?</font>

191
00:11:56,270 --> 00:11:58,040
<font color="yellow">Here.</font>

192
00:11:59,340 --> 00:12:00,400
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

193
00:12:04,270 --> 00:12:05,900
<font color="yellow">- Mr Kang. - Jun.</font>

194
00:12:06,370 --> 00:12:08,840
<font color="yellow">- Do you want to work at a cabaret? - A cabaret?</font>

195
00:12:08,870 --> 00:12:12,940
<font color="yellow">Someone I know manages one, and he's looking for a singer.</font>

196
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:19,640
<font color="yellow">You value your pride too much. You'd never sing at a cabaret.</font>

197
00:12:20,170 --> 00:12:21,700
<font color="yellow">- Forget I asked. - I'll do it.</font>

198
00:12:22,040 --> 00:12:25,170
<font color="yellow">I'll go anywhere that'll let me sing.</font>

199
00:12:25,970 --> 00:12:28,400
<font color="yellow">How about I start tonight?</font>

200
00:12:30,300 --> 00:12:31,300
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

201
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:36,770
<font color="yellow">He used to say he wanted to make suits until the day he died.</font>

202
00:12:37,800 --> 00:12:40,240
<font color="yellow">I don't understand why he wants to retire.</font>

203
00:12:42,300 --> 00:12:45,300
<font color="yellow">He worked hard his whole life.</font>

204
00:12:45,970 --> 00:12:48,940
<font color="yellow">I think we should let him take a break.</font>

205
00:12:54,170 --> 00:12:56,740
<font color="yellow">What? Do you have something to say?</font>

206
00:12:57,340 --> 00:12:58,700
<font color="yellow">Not. It's nothing.</font>

207
00:13:07,340 --> 00:13:10,700
<font color="yellow">He looks really angry. What should I do?</font>

208
00:13:13,300 --> 00:13:16,440
<font color="yellow">Why did I ask such a stupid question?</font>

