00:15:16,270 --> 00:15:17,370
<font color="yellow">Make me two.</font>

235
00:15:17,770 --> 00:15:20,170
<font color="yellow">I'm going to show them to my colleagues in Milan.</font>

236
00:15:20,170 --> 00:15:22,070
<font color="yellow">I'll keep one for myself...</font>

237
00:15:22,170 --> 00:15:24,770
<font color="yellow">and give one to the company as a sample.</font>

238
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,700
<font color="yellow">What did he say?</font>

