268
00:17:33,740 --> 00:17:36,300
<font color="yellow">Why else would we cross paths?</font>

269
00:17:38,270 --> 00:17:40,300
<font color="yellow">I wanted to keep an eye on you.</font>

270
00:17:40,870 --> 00:17:44,500
<font color="yellow">I wanted to see who she'd been blindly in love with...</font>

271
00:17:44,970 --> 00:17:48,670
<font color="yellow">and if there were residual feelings I should be concerned about.</font>

272
00:17:48,900 --> 00:17:50,170
<font color="yellow">I wanted to clear that up.</font>

273
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:52,270
<font color="yellow">You used me, then.</font>

274
00:17:52,610 --> 00:17:54,270
<font color="yellow">In a way, yes.</font>

275
00:17:54,470 --> 00:17:56,170
<font color="yellow">I will resign.</font>

276
00:17:56,970 --> 00:17:59,500
<font color="yellow">I tendered my resignation to Ms Min.</font>

277
00:18:01,640 --> 00:18:04,270
<font color="yellow">I don't think you're in any position to put your pride first.</font>

278
00:18:04,270 --> 00:18:06,770
<font color="yellow">I'm not quitting out of pride.</font>

279
00:18:07,340 --> 00:18:09,840
<font color="yellow">It's because I see this company has no future.</font>

280
00:18:10,040 --> 00:18:12,440
<font color="yellow">- What? - You hire staff...</font>

281
00:18:12,440 --> 00:18:14,640
<font color="yellow">out of curiosity about your girlfriend's exes,</font>

282
00:18:14,900 --> 00:18:17,700
<font color="yellow">and you steal a competitor's clothes during a competition.</font>

283
00:18:18,240 --> 00:18:21,700
<font color="yellow">I won't work for a corrupt CEO with no vision whatsoever.</font>

284
00:18:22,070 --> 00:18:23,340
<font color="yellow">How dare you.</font>

285
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:25,570
<font color="yellow">Good bye.</font>

286
00:18:35,400 --> 00:18:36,500
<font color="yellow">Kang Tae Yang.</font>

287
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:42,400
<font color="yellow">You came in freely, but you can't leave on your own terms.</font>

288
00:18:49,500 --> 00:18:51,370
<font color="yellow">You dared to make the first move?</font>

289
00:18:53,040 --> 00:18:55,170
<font color="yellow">I won't let you go so easily.</font>

290
00:19:12,300 --> 00:19:13,400
<font color="yellow">What do you think you're doing?</font>

