292
00:19:14,870 --> 00:19:17,110
<font color="yellow">I marked you as mine.</font>

293
00:19:17,700 --> 00:19:19,610
<font color="yellow">Kang Tae Yang is mine now.</font>

294
00:19:19,840 --> 00:19:22,570
<font color="yellow">I'm not going to let anyone else take you away from me.</font>

295
00:19:22,770 --> 00:19:26,110
