296
00:19:26,340 --> 00:19:28,640
<font color="yellow">the purest person I've ever met.</font>

297
00:19:29,270 --> 00:19:30,540
<font color="yellow">But that's about it.</font>

298
00:19:30,940 --> 00:19:32,870
<font color="yellow">I don't have any more feelings.</font>

299
00:19:36,970 --> 00:19:38,300
<font color="yellow">What a jerk.</font>

300
00:19:42,540 --> 00:19:44,040
<font color="yellow">Is she crying?</font>

301
00:19:44,540 --> 00:19:45,640
<font color="yellow">What about?</font>

302
00:19:45,740 --> 00:19:47,840
<font color="yellow">I think something's wrong.</font>

303
00:20:04,140 --> 00:20:05,610
<font color="yellow">Is something wrong?</font>

304
00:20:06,470 --> 00:20:10,470
<font color="yellow">It's Ms Min. She won't stop crying.</font>

305
00:20:13,640 --> 00:20:14,700
<font color="yellow">Oh, dear.</font>

306
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:26,440
<font color="yellow">Ms Min.</font>

307
00:20:32,800 --> 00:20:33,800
<font color="yellow">Ms Min.</font>

308
00:20:35,800 --> 00:20:36,940
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

309
00:20:36,940 --> 00:20:39,840
<font color="yellow">Why are you crying in front of your staff?</font>

310
00:20:40,040 --> 00:20:42,070
<font color="yellow">Who said I was crying?</font>

311
00:20:48,470 --> 00:20:51,640
<font color="yellow">Don't get the wrong idea, people. My eyes are sore.</font>

312
00:20:53,040 --> 00:20:54,840
<font color="yellow">- They hurt bad. - Okay.</font>

313
00:20:54,840 --> 00:20:56,110
<font color="yellow">- Okay. - Okay.</font>

314
00:21:08,370 --> 00:21:11,000
<font color="yellow">You should know what I'm crying about.</font>

315
00:21:11,470 --> 00:21:12,870
<font color="yellow">Now you comfort me?</font>

316
00:21:23,170 --> 00:21:24,540
<font color="yellow">(Sample Request)</font>

317
00:21:24,940 --> 00:21:27,300
<font color="yellow">- What is it? - A sample request form.</font>

318
00:21:28,140 --> 00:21:31,570
<font color="yellow">I have to send them to suppliers and relevant departments.</font>

319
00:21:31,870 --> 00:21:33,800
<font color="yellow">I requested 10 of each.</font>

320
00:21:38,300 --> 00:21:42,340
<font color="yellow">(Min Hyo Won)</font>

321
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:46,610
<font color="yellow">I'll take it to the CEO.</font>

322
00:21:51,940 --> 00:21:53,640
<font color="yellow">What a horrible eye infection.</font>

323
00:21:59,440 --> 00:22:02,240
<font color="yellow">I'm sure it's not an infection. Did she get dumped?</font>

324
00:22:02,340 --> 00:22:05,170
<font color="yellow">- Maybe. It looks serious. - It does.</font>

325
00:22:05,870 --> 00:22:06,940
<font color="yellow">Come in.</font>

326
00:22:12,870 --> 00:22:15,400
<font color="yellow">You wanted to see all the papers I sign.</font>

327
00:22:15,500 --> 00:22:17,970
<font color="yellow">- Here's my sample request form. - Let me see.</font>

328
00:22:19,870 --> 00:22:21,170
