00:22:28,100 --> 00:22:30,000
<font color="yellow">No. Mind your own business.</font>

332
00:22:31,870 --> 00:22:33,470
<font color="yellow">She's in a rotten mood.</font>

333
00:22:37,040 --> 00:22:39,140
<font color="yellow">(Sample Request)</font>

