335
00:22:45,970 --> 00:22:48,240
<font color="yellow">Hello, Madam Ko.</font>

336
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:50,770
<font color="yellow">Is Choi Ji Yun here?</font>

337
00:22:50,770 --> 00:22:53,300
<font color="yellow">Yes. She's getting her hair done.</font>

338
00:22:54,070 --> 00:22:55,270
<font color="yellow">You didn't tell her that I was coming, right?</font>

339
00:22:55,370 --> 00:22:59,440
<font color="yellow">Of course not. You told me to keep my mouth shut.</font>

340
00:22:59,740 --> 00:23:00,800
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

341
00:23:02,470 --> 00:23:03,700
<font color="yellow">Let's have a look.</font>

342
00:23:03,870 --> 00:23:05,070
<font color="yellow">Take a seat.</font>

343
00:23:10,040 --> 00:23:11,300
<font color="yellow">Some tea, Madam?</font>

344
00:23:11,300 --> 00:23:13,070
<font color="yellow">Yes, I'll have some rooibos.</font>

345
00:23:13,300 --> 00:23:14,300
<font color="yellow">Sure.</font>

346
00:23:14,800 --> 00:23:15,870
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

347
00:23:16,370 --> 00:23:17,370
<font color="yellow">Hi.</font>

348
00:23:18,240 --> 00:23:19,770
<font color="yellow">- Hello. - Hi.</font>

349
00:23:19,770 --> 00:23:22,040
<font color="yellow">Do you have a specific style in mind?</font>

350
00:23:22,270 --> 00:23:23,540
<font color="yellow">No. Just fix it a little bit.</font>

351
00:23:23,640 --> 00:23:24,700
<font color="yellow">Sure.</font>

352
00:23:35,600 --> 00:23:36,770
<font color="yellow">That's hot.</font>

353
00:23:37,270 --> 00:23:39,770
<font color="yellow">My goodness. I'm really sorry.</font>

354
00:23:42,340 --> 00:23:44,170
<font color="yellow">I don't think it touched your skin, though.</font>

355
00:23:44,640 --> 00:23:46,300
<font color="yellow">Are you calling me a liar?</font>

356
00:23:46,540 --> 00:23:48,870
<font color="yellow">- No. - It's hot if I say it is.</font>

357
00:23:49,500 --> 00:23:50,670
<font color="yellow">Give me a mirror.</font>

358
00:23:51,800 --> 00:23:52,900
<font color="yellow">Yes, Miss.</font>

359
00:23:58,770 --> 00:24:00,570
<font color="yellow">What if I end up with a scar?</font>

360
00:24:00,800 --> 00:24:02,470
<font color="yellow">Can't you be more careful?</font>

361
00:24:02,470 --> 00:24:03,800
<font color="yellow">I didn't touch...</font>

362
00:24:05,370 --> 00:24:08,940
<font color="yellow">I apologise. I'll give you free hair treatment to make up for it.</font>

363
00:24:09,770 --> 00:24:11,400
<font color="yellow">That's not the problem.</font>

364
00:24:12,040 --> 00:24:13,470
<font color="yellow">I tie my hair up often.</font>

365
00:24:13,470 --> 00:24:15,140
<font color="yellow">What if I end up with a scar on my neck?</font>

366
00:24:15,240 --> 00:24:17,470
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry. I'll be more careful from now on.</font>

367
00:24:18,100 --> 00:24:20,140
<font color="yellow">You even singed my hair last time.</font>

368
00:24:20,540 --> 00:24:21,940
<font color="yellow">You do nothing right.</font>

369
00:24:22,170 --> 00:24:23,540
<font color="yellow">Da Jeong's...</font>

370
00:24:24,170 --> 00:24:26,000
<font color="yellow">one of the better ones here.</font>

371
00:24:29,270 --> 00:24:33,240
<font color="yellow">She's pretty good at her job and serves her clients well.</font>

372
00:24:37,800 --> 00:24:38,900
<font color="yellow">Manager.</font>

373
00:24:39,500 --> 00:24:42,170
<font color="yellow">- Yes, Miss? - Get me another stylist.</font>

374
00:24:42,600 --> 00:24:44,600
<font color="yellow">I can't trust her with my hair.</font>

375
00:24:45,070 --> 00:24:46,240
<font color="yellow">I understand.</font>

376
00:24:46,440 --> 00:24:48,340
<font color="yellow">Go to the shampoo room.</font>

377
00:24:48,540 --> 00:24:49,840
<font color="yellow">Yes, Ma'am.</font>

378
00:24:50,970 --> 00:24:54,170
<font color="yellow">Someone has a nasty temper for a young lady.</font>

379
00:24:55,270 --> 00:24:58,640
<font color="yellow">Are you talking about me?</font>

