00:25:03,470 --> 00:25:04,640
<font color="yellow">What the...</font>

381
00:25:12,570 --> 00:25:14,270
<font color="yellow">- Hello? - Madam Ko.</font>

382
00:25:14,270 --> 00:25:16,400
<font color="yellow">It's me, Bok Sun Nyeo.</font>

383
00:25:17,240 --> 00:25:18,240
