384
00:25:18,240 --> 00:25:20,170
<font color="yellow">Have you forgotten my name already?</font>

385
00:25:20,670 --> 00:25:22,940
<font color="yellow">I'm Bae Sam Do's wife.</font>

386
00:25:23,040 --> 00:25:25,070
<font color="yellow">Why are you calling me?</font>

387
00:25:51,500 --> 00:25:52,840
<font color="yellow">Hello, Madam Ko.</font>

388
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:56,100
<font color="yellow">What business do you have with me?</font>

389
00:25:56,400 --> 00:25:59,000
<font color="yellow">I promised you that I'd bring you some kimchi,</font>

390
00:25:59,170 --> 00:26:02,100
<font color="yellow">but life got in the way and I forgot about it.</font>

391
00:26:02,700 --> 00:26:04,940
<font color="yellow">You seemed to like my Korean lettuce kimchi,</font>

392
00:26:04,940 --> 00:26:07,440
<font color="yellow">so I brought you some as they're perfectly ripe.</font>

393
00:26:19,840 --> 00:26:20,940
<font color="yellow">Is everything okay?</font>

394
00:26:21,040 --> 00:26:22,670
<font color="yellow">Something happened recently.</font>

395
00:26:25,770 --> 00:26:27,440
<font color="yellow">What happened?</font>

396
00:26:27,440 --> 00:26:30,040
<font color="yellow">Mr Lee came home last night.</font>

397
00:26:30,570 --> 00:26:32,170
<font color="yellow">- Did he? - Yes.</font>

398
00:26:32,640 --> 00:26:35,140
<font color="yellow">Also, my husband won the most prestigious award...</font>

399
00:26:35,140 --> 00:26:37,670
<font color="yellow">at the Bespoke Suit Tailoring Competition,</font>

400
00:26:37,870 --> 00:26:39,740
<font color="yellow">so we all celebrated last night.</font>

401
00:26:41,140 --> 00:26:45,570
<font color="yellow">Where was Mr Lee and what was he up to all this while?</font>

402
00:26:46,240 --> 00:26:48,700
<font color="yellow">He travelled the country...</font>

403
00:26:48,700 --> 00:26:52,270
<font color="yellow">and made free suits for people who couldn't afford one.</font>

404
00:26:52,370 --> 00:26:55,540
<font color="yellow">He goes out of his way to make his life harder.</font>

405
00:26:56,500 --> 00:26:58,670
<font color="yellow">What's that handbag?</font>

406
00:27:01,240 --> 00:27:06,470
<font color="yellow">This isn't the real reason I came to see you, but...</font>

407
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:08,040
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

408
00:27:08,040 --> 00:27:11,170
<font color="yellow">I bought it at a department store yesterday.</font>

409
00:27:11,740 --> 00:27:15,000
<font color="yellow">Could you buy this off me?</font>

410
00:27:15,100 --> 00:27:17,340
<font color="yellow">I'll give you a 10-percent discount.</font>

411
00:27:17,670 --> 00:27:19,000
<font color="yellow">Why should I buy yours?</font>

412
00:27:19,100 --> 00:27:22,540
<font color="yellow">I swear that I only used it for one day.</font>

413
00:27:22,640 --> 00:27:25,340
<font color="yellow">I practically hugged it when I walked,</font>

414
00:27:25,340 --> 00:27:27,140
<font color="yellow">so there are no scratches.</font>

415
00:27:31,740 --> 00:27:35,240
<font color="yellow">No thanks. I don't even like the brand.</font>

416
00:27:35,670 --> 00:27:39,140
<font color="yellow">Then I'll give you a 20-percent discount.</font>

417
00:27:40,540 --> 00:27:42,440
<font color="yellow">Are you trying to bargain with me?</font>

418
00:27:42,640 --> 00:27:44,740
<font color="yellow">Of all the people I know,</font>

419
00:27:45,000 --> 00:27:48,100
<font color="yellow">you're the only one deserving of this handbag.</font>

420
00:27:48,440 --> 00:27:50,540
