00:27:53,800 --> 00:27:57,340
<font color="yellow">Why did you buy a bag you won't even use?</font>

423
00:27:57,870 --> 00:28:01,870
<font color="yellow">I bought it out of spite after getting into a fight with Sam Do.</font>

424
00:28:02,540 --> 00:28:05,800
