431
00:28:33,040 --> 00:28:37,070
<font color="yellow">But why doesn't he want to have children?</font>

432
00:28:37,870 --> 00:28:40,640
<font color="yellow">He said it's because...</font>

433
00:28:40,870 --> 00:28:44,770
