434
00:28:45,070 --> 00:28:47,900
<font color="yellow">He said it's for my sake.</font>

435
00:28:48,170 --> 00:28:49,300
<font color="yellow">Wait.</font>

436
00:28:50,270 --> 00:28:52,470
<font color="yellow">Does he still miss Young Eun?</font>

437
00:28:52,700 --> 00:28:53,970
<font color="yellow">Who's Young Eun?</font>

438
00:28:54,070 --> 00:28:55,240
<font color="yellow">His first love.</font>

439
00:28:55,340 --> 00:28:58,570
<font color="yellow">His what? He had a first love?</font>

440
00:28:58,670 --> 00:29:02,870
<font color="yellow">Of course. Why wouldn't he, with his looks and build?</font>

441
00:29:02,870 --> 00:29:05,940
<font color="yellow">He told me that I was his first love.</font>

442
00:29:08,170 --> 00:29:09,340
<font color="yellow">No way.</font>

443
00:29:11,470 --> 00:29:14,640
<font color="yellow">He brought her to the tailor shop a few times a long time ago...</font>

444
00:29:14,640 --> 00:29:17,440
<font color="yellow">and introduced her to Mr Lee and me.</font>

445
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:19,100
<font color="yellow">Who is that witch?</font>

446
00:29:19,640 --> 00:29:20,770
<font color="yellow">You startled me.</font>

447
00:29:20,770 --> 00:29:23,470
<font color="yellow">So who is that witch?</font>

448
00:29:24,370 --> 00:29:27,700
<font color="yellow">They grew up together in the same orphanage.</font>

449
00:29:27,970 --> 00:29:31,070
<font color="yellow">She was pretty and nice.</font>

450
00:29:31,640 --> 00:29:32,770
<font color="yellow">She used to smile a lot, too.</font>

451
00:29:32,770 --> 00:29:34,770
<font color="yellow">Where is that witch now?</font>

452
00:29:35,040 --> 00:29:36,900
<font color="yellow">Do you have to call her like that?</font>

453
00:29:36,900 --> 00:29:40,870
<font color="yellow">Where is that woman now?</font>

454
00:29:41,270 --> 00:29:43,170
<font color="yellow">How would I know?</font>

455
00:29:43,540 --> 00:29:47,500
<font color="yellow">I think I heard that she moved to Seattle after she got married.</font>

456
00:29:48,340 --> 00:29:49,470
<font color="yellow">Goodness.</font>

457
00:29:52,070 --> 00:29:54,800
<font color="yellow">Should I not have brought it up?</font>

458
00:29:55,800 --> 00:29:59,540
<font color="yellow">Well... It wasn't anything serious.</font>

459
00:29:59,740 --> 00:30:01,870
<font color="yellow">I'm sure it was just puppy love.</font>

460
00:30:02,270 --> 00:30:04,340
<font color="yellow">Don't tell Sam Do...</font>

461
00:30:04,440 --> 00:30:07,840
<font color="yellow">that I told you this, okay?</font>

462
00:30:10,100 --> 00:30:13,170
<font color="yellow">Oh, that's right. I'll buy this purse from you,</font>

463
00:30:13,500 --> 00:30:16,000
<font color="yellow">so don't tell Sam Do.</font>

464
00:30:16,370 --> 00:30:18,400
<font color="yellow">Just pretend that you didn't hear anything.</font>

465
00:30:19,500 --> 00:30:20,940
<font color="yellow">How much do you want for the purse?</font>

466
00:30:21,900 --> 00:30:23,470
<font color="yellow">- 2,000... - 2,000?</font>

467
00:30:24,100 --> 00:30:25,600
<font color="yellow">2,300 dollars.</font>

468
00:30:32,140 --> 00:30:33,170
<font color="yellow">I'm home.</font>

469
00:30:33,900 --> 00:30:37,040
<font color="yellow">People at the shop told me that you left a while ago.</font>

470
00:30:37,140 --> 00:30:38,700
<font color="yellow">Where have you been?</font>

471
00:30:38,800 --> 00:30:41,540
<font color="yellow">I had to take care of something. Have a seat.</font>

472
00:30:49,640 --> 00:30:50,940
<font color="yellow">What is this?</font>

473
00:30:54,440 --> 00:30:56,600
<font color="yellow">What are these rings for?</font>

474
00:30:57,440 --> 00:30:59,540
<font color="yellow">I thought about it...</font>

475
00:31:00,470 --> 00:31:04,640
<font color="yellow">and realised that I have never given you a ring.</font>

476
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:07,700
<font color="yellow">When we got married, I couldn't afford it.</font>

477
00:31:07,840 --> 00:31:11,100
<font color="yellow">And since then, we've been preoccupied with running the shop...</font>

478
00:31:11,100 --> 00:31:14,640
<font color="yellow">and raising our kids while trying to make ends meet.</font>

479
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:16,070
<font color="yellow">Honey.</font>

480
00:31:16,370 --> 00:31:19,640
<font color="yellow">I appreciate everything you've done, and I'm sorry that it's so late.</font>

481
00:31:19,640 --> 00:31:20,970
<font color="yellow">I got two rings for you...</font>

482
00:31:20,970 --> 00:31:23,170
<font color="yellow">to make up for keeping you waiting for so long.</font>

483
00:31:26,970 --> 00:31:28,240
<font color="yellow">Try them on.</font>

484
00:31:33,100 --> 00:31:37,170
<font color="yellow">Oh, my! They fit perfectly.</font>

485
00:31:37,370 --> 00:31:39,670
<font color="yellow">I've lived with you for long enough to know.</font>

486
00:31:39,940 --> 00:31:42,300
<font color="yellow">It looks like your little deviation away from home...</font>

487
00:31:42,440 --> 00:31:44,740
<font color="yellow">has matured you a lot.</font>

488
00:31:48,270 --> 00:31:51,470
<font color="yellow">I can't even recognise my hand with these rings on.</font>

489
00:31:51,770 --> 00:31:54,500
<font color="yellow">It looks like it belongs to a woman from a very wealthy family.</font>

490
00:31:54,840 --> 00:31:55,900
<font color="yellow">Are you that happy?</font>

491
00:31:56,040 --> 00:31:57,570
<font color="yellow">Of course I'm happy.</font>

492
00:31:58,070 --> 00:32:02,170
<font color="yellow">You've never given me a ring before.</font>

493
00:32:07,470 --> 00:32:10,770
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry. I should've been more affectionate.</font>

494
00:32:11,340 --> 00:32:14,700
<font color="yellow">How about you leave again?</font>

495
00:32:14,940 --> 00:32:15,970
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

496
00:32:16,340 --> 00:32:20,640
<font color="yellow">You gave me two rings this time. If you leave again,</font>

497
00:32:21,370 --> 00:32:23,670
<font color="yellow">you might come back with a gold necklace.</font>

498
00:32:25,440 --> 00:32:26,470
<font color="yellow">You silly.</font>

499
00:32:50,970 --> 00:32:52,870
<font color="yellow">- Would you like a cup of tea? - No, thanks.</font>

500
00:32:53,170 --> 00:32:54,570
<font color="yellow">I just came to get a glass of water.</font>

501
00:32:57,270 --> 00:33:00,400
<font color="yellow">I was just kidding earlier.</font>

502
00:33:01,540 --> 00:33:05,240
<font color="yellow">I just said it as a joke, but you took it so seriously.</font>

503
00:33:05,600 --> 00:33:07,300
<font color="yellow">Your reaction got me all flustered.</font>

504
00:33:08,140 --> 00:33:11,070
<font color="yellow">You don't need to worry about it at all.</font>

505
00:33:18,570 --> 00:33:20,840
<font color="yellow">Why is he being like that? Doesn't he know that I'm embarrassed?</font>

506
00:33:21,170 --> 00:33:25,300
<font color="yellow">Can't he just pretend to believe that it was a joke?</font>

507
00:33:34,300 --> 00:33:36,100
<font color="yellow">Gosh, this is stressing me out.</font>

508
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:38,470
<font color="yellow">I mean, it's Italy's top suit brand.</font>

509
00:33:38,670 --> 00:33:40,700
<font color="yellow">I'm making a suit for the head designer there.</font>

510
00:33:40,900 --> 00:33:43,600
<font color="yellow">It's like teaching a fish how to swim.</font>

511
00:33:43,600 --> 00:33:45,100
<font color="yellow">Don't think like that.</font>

512
00:33:45,300 --> 00:33:48,170
<font color="yellow">You could have something Italian craftsmen don't have.</font>

513
00:33:48,170 --> 00:33:51,670
<font color="yellow">No. I think I should ask Mr Lee to make this suit.</font>

514
00:33:51,870 --> 00:33:55,800
<font color="yellow">What if I make a mistake and ruin our shop's name globally?</font>

515
00:33:56,140 --> 00:34:00,000
<font color="yellow">Gianni fell in love with your suit at the competition.</font>

516
00:34:00,300 --> 00:34:02,840
<font color="yellow">Don't worry too much and just put your skills to use.</font>

517
00:34:05,400 --> 00:34:07,170
<font color="yellow">- Hey, Yun Shil. - Yes, Master.</font>

518
00:34:07,400 --> 00:34:09,940
<font color="yellow">I wrote down the fabrics and materials I need on this order form.</font>

519
00:34:10,270 --> 00:34:12,010
<font color="yellow">Can you go to the fabric market and get them for me?</font>

520
00:34:12,370 --> 00:34:13,940
<font color="yellow">It'll be a very expensive suit.</font>

521
00:34:13,940 --> 00:34:17,800
<font color="yellow">I'd like you to feel the fabrics and check everything in person.</font>

522
00:34:18,070 --> 00:34:19,840
<font color="yellow">- Sure. - Dong Jin, you should go with her.</font>

523
00:34:19,970 --> 00:34:21,470
<font color="yellow">Just take a taxi, Yun Shil.</font>

524
00:34:21,670 --> 00:34:24,170
<font color="yellow">I have to take care of something urgently.</font>

525
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:37,670
<font color="yellow">I'm going to the market.</font>

526
00:34:37,670 --> 00:34:38,940
<font color="yellow">Okay. See you later.</font>

527
00:34:47,100 --> 00:34:48,170
<font color="yellow">Well,</font>

528
00:34:48,940 --> 00:34:51,040
<font color="yellow">I know I said that I was joking earlier,</font>

529
00:34:51,840 --> 00:34:53,670
<font color="yellow">but I actually wasn't.</font>

530
00:34:55,270 --> 00:34:58,570
<font color="yellow">You've been so nice to me,</font>

