00:34:58,940 --> 00:35:00,570
<font color="yellow">so I got the wrong idea.</font>

532
00:35:01,040 --> 00:35:03,640
<font color="yellow">People can get wrong ideas at times, you know.</font>

533
00:35:05,170 --> 00:35:09,040
<font color="yellow">I apologised to you in person as well as via text.</font>

534
00:35:09,470 --> 00:35:11,470
<font color="yellow">Do you have to make me feel embarrassed like this?</font>

535
00:35:11,470 --> 00:35:12,700
<font color="yellow">I should've been...</font>

536
00:35:14,100 --> 00:35:15,670
<font color="yellow">more thoughtful.</font>

537
00:35:16,770 --> 00:35:19,570
<font color="yellow">- Pardon me? - I was just worried as a co-worker.</font>

538
00:35:19,940 --> 00:35:21,640
<font color="yellow">That's why I treated you like that.</font>

539
00:35:21,970 --> 00:35:25,600
<font color="yellow">I guess my acts of kindness made you get the wrong idea.</font>

540
00:35:27,770 --> 00:35:29,640
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry for giving you the wrong impression.</font>

541
00:35:30,100 --> 00:35:31,570
<font color="yellow">I'll be careful from now on.</font>

542
00:35:38,070 --> 00:35:41,300
<font color="yellow">You don't need to apologise.</font>

543
00:35:42,600 --> 00:35:46,670
<font color="yellow">I talked nonsense to you like a fool.</font>

544
00:35:48,800 --> 00:35:50,170
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

545
00:36:10,070 --> 00:36:11,600
<font color="yellow">Yes, I did the right thing.</font>

546
00:36:12,270 --> 00:36:16,170
<font color="yellow">I can't have her think that I'm leading her on.</font>

547
00:36:44,700 --> 00:36:46,600
<font color="yellow">What are you doing here?</font>

548
00:36:46,600 --> 00:36:48,470
<font color="yellow">I was waiting for you.</font>

549
00:36:49,370 --> 00:36:52,040
<font color="yellow">Why were you waiting for me?</font>

550
00:36:52,040 --> 00:36:53,770
<font color="yellow">You keep crying at work...</font>

551
00:36:54,140 --> 00:36:56,800
<font color="yellow">and skipping meals. I feel like it's my fault, so I got worried.</font>

552
00:36:56,800 --> 00:36:58,640
<font color="yellow">I thought I made it clear.</font>

553
00:36:59,740 --> 00:37:03,140
<font color="yellow">I may cling onto you again if you're nice to me.</font>

554
00:37:03,140 --> 00:37:07,570
<font color="yellow">I'm going to erase all memories of that day.</font>

555
00:37:08,100 --> 00:37:09,570
<font color="yellow">You should forget about it, too.</font>

556
00:37:10,240 --> 00:37:11,510
<font color="yellow">How can I forget?</font>

557
00:37:14,510 --> 00:37:15,800
<font color="yellow">It was my first kiss.</font>

558
00:37:17,240 --> 00:37:19,240
<font color="yellow">First kiss?</font>

559
00:37:20,670 --> 00:37:22,510
<font color="yellow">It wasn't your first kiss, was it?</font>

560
00:37:23,240 --> 00:37:24,300
<font color="yellow">Of course...</font>

561
00:37:26,300 --> 00:37:27,300
<font color="yellow">it wasn't.</font>

562
00:37:27,770 --> 00:37:29,900
<font color="yellow">See? I knew it.</font>

563
00:37:30,510 --> 00:37:32,800
<font color="yellow">Then how many girls have you kissed? Where am I on your list?</font>

564
00:37:32,940 --> 00:37:34,640
<font color="yellow">That's such an inappropriate question.</font>

565
00:37:35,840 --> 00:37:36,870
<font color="yellow">Second?</font>

566
00:37:38,270 --> 00:37:39,300
<font color="yellow">Or...</font>

567
00:37:40,840 --> 00:37:42,010
<font color="yellow">Third?</font>

568
00:37:44,170 --> 00:37:47,510
<font color="yellow">No? You can't count with the fingers of both hands?</font>

569
00:37:47,870 --> 00:37:49,040
<font color="yellow">Enough.</font>

570
00:37:49,600 --> 00:37:53,170
<font color="yellow">It's my loss. My poor lips.</font>

571
00:37:54,010 --> 00:37:55,170
<font color="yellow">I better get going now.</font>

572
00:37:55,170 --> 00:37:57,600
<font color="yellow">Where do you think you're going?</font>

573
00:37:57,970 --> 00:37:59,940
<font color="yellow">Take responsibility for what you've done, you jerk!</font>

574
00:38:15,370 --> 00:38:16,470
<font color="yellow">Are you all right?</font>

575
00:38:19,970 --> 00:38:22,970
<font color="yellow">- What's wrong? - I think I hurt my back.</font>

576
00:38:24,640 --> 00:38:26,010
<font color="yellow">Gosh, what should I do?</font>

577
00:38:27,940 --> 00:38:30,540
<font color="yellow">- I can't get up. - Really?</font>

578
00:38:35,040 --> 00:38:36,140
<font color="yellow">Ouch.</font>

579
00:38:40,240 --> 00:38:41,440
<font color="yellow">Please be gentle.</font>

580
00:38:43,070 --> 00:38:44,140
<font color="yellow">Hold on a second.</font>

581
00:38:44,600 --> 00:38:47,570
<font color="yellow">- Why? - Just a second. I'm in pain.</font>

582
00:39:09,140 --> 00:39:11,040
<font color="yellow">We're here. Get off.</font>

583
00:39:19,340 --> 00:39:22,470
<font color="yellow">I can't get up by myself. Help me get up.</font>

584
00:39:35,600 --> 00:39:36,600
<font color="yellow">What's wrong?</font>

585
00:39:36,700 --> 00:39:37,800
<font color="yellow">Ouch.</font>

586
00:39:38,170 --> 00:39:39,600
<font color="yellow">I can't get up.</font>

587
00:39:39,800 --> 00:39:42,270
<font color="yellow">Why not? You were fine when you were walking out of the hospital.</font>

588
00:39:42,270 --> 00:39:44,270
<font color="yellow">I was okay earlier because it was right after I got a shot,</font>

589
00:39:44,270 --> 00:39:46,170
<font color="yellow">but it's hurting again now.</font>

590
00:39:47,370 --> 00:39:51,170
<font color="yellow">What's that look? I fell because of you. How can you be so mean?</font>

591
00:39:52,070 --> 00:39:53,770
<font color="yellow">I'm not trying to be mean.</font>

592
00:39:54,070 --> 00:39:55,840
<font color="yellow">What do you want me to do, then?</font>

593
00:39:57,170 --> 00:39:59,770
<font color="yellow">- Carry me. - I beg your pardon?</font>

594
00:39:59,970 --> 00:40:01,770
<font color="yellow">Carry me to my room.</font>

595
00:40:01,870 --> 00:40:03,070
<font color="yellow">Ms Min.</font>

596
00:40:03,400 --> 00:40:06,240
<font color="yellow">I can't even get up. What am I supposed to do?</font>

597
00:40:06,540 --> 00:40:07,740
<font color="yellow">Shall I stay in the car all night?</font>

598
00:40:07,840 --> 00:40:08,970
<font color="yellow">Well...</font>

599
00:40:16,600 --> 00:40:19,940
<font color="yellow">Ms Min, what happened?</font>

600
00:40:20,510 --> 00:40:22,240
<font color="yellow">Please open the door.</font>

601
00:40:22,340 --> 00:40:23,340
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

602
00:40:25,600 --> 00:40:26,600
<font color="yellow">Is it Hyo Won or Hyo Sang?</font>

603
00:40:26,600 --> 00:40:27,870
<font color="yellow">It's Ms Min.</font>

604
00:40:28,070 --> 00:40:31,040
<font color="yellow">But some guy is carrying her.</font>

605
00:40:31,470 --> 00:40:33,740
<font color="yellow">A guy is carrying her? What do you mean?</font>

606
00:40:36,800 --> 00:40:37,840
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

607
00:40:39,400 --> 00:40:41,470
<font color="yellow">What happened to her?</font>

608
00:40:41,670 --> 00:40:43,640
<font color="yellow">What did you do to Hyo Won?</font>

609
00:40:43,840 --> 00:40:45,300
<font color="yellow">Mr Kang didn't do anything wrong.</font>

610
00:40:45,510 --> 00:40:47,340
<font color="yellow">I accidentally fell in the parking lot.</font>

611
00:40:48,240 --> 00:40:50,670
<font color="yellow">I fell on my behind and hurt my back a little.</font>

612
00:40:50,770 --> 00:40:53,070
<font color="yellow">- What? - I took her to a hospital.</font>

613
00:40:53,170 --> 00:40:55,170
<font color="yellow">The doctor said that it's not a serious injury.</font>

614
00:40:55,400 --> 00:40:58,870
<font color="yellow">She just needs a few physiotherapy sessions, so please don't worry.</font>

615
00:40:59,700 --> 00:41:01,540
<font color="yellow">Tae Yang. You haven't been to our place before, right?</font>

616
00:41:01,840 --> 00:41:03,440
<font color="yellow">My room is upstairs.</font>

617
00:41:04,240 --> 00:41:05,370
<font color="yellow">Sorry.</font>

618
00:41:06,040 --> 00:41:07,040
<font color="yellow">My gosh.</font>

619
00:41:08,840 --> 00:41:11,740
<font color="yellow">What is that girl thinking?</font>

620
00:41:14,640 --> 00:41:15,640
<font color="yellow">Gosh!</font>

621
00:41:15,640 --> 00:41:18,400
<font color="yellow">- Goodness. - Are you all right, Madam?</font>

622
00:41:19,010 --> 00:41:20,440
<font color="yellow">Leave me alone.</font>

623
00:41:38,640 --> 00:41:40,940
<font color="yellow">Thanks. Am I too heavy?</font>

624
00:41:41,270 --> 00:41:42,540
<font color="yellow">No, it was fine.</font>

625
00:41:43,140 --> 00:41:44,970
<font color="yellow">You don't look fine at all.</font>

626
00:41:45,240 --> 00:41:47,470
<font color="yellow">You're sweating so much. Gosh.</font>

627
00:41:49,070 --> 00:41:50,240
<font color="yellow">Halt!</font>

628
00:41:55,070 --> 00:41:56,100
<font color="yellow">You two.</font>

629
00:41:56,900 --> 00:41:58,100
<font color="yellow">What were you just doing?</font>

630
00:41:58,100 --> 00:42:01,100
<font color="yellow">We weren't doing anything. He just put me in bed.</font>

631
00:42:01,970 --> 00:42:03,170
<font color="yellow">Thanks for today.</font>

632
00:42:03,270 --> 00:42:06,570
<font color="yellow">I would've had to call the ambulance if you weren't there.</font>

633
00:42:06,870 --> 00:42:08,740
<font color="yellow">Are you actually injured?</font>

634
00:42:08,900 --> 00:42:11,010
<font color="yellow">Yes, I told you. Here, look.</font>

635
00:42:11,540 --> 00:42:14,740
<font color="yellow">The doctor even gave me medication.</font>

636
00:42:14,840 --> 00:42:15,970
<font color="yellow">Ouch, my back...</font>

637
00:42:17,010 --> 00:42:18,170
<font color="yellow">I'm in pain.</font>

638
00:42:19,670 --> 00:42:21,140
<font color="yellow">I should get going now.</font>

639
00:42:25,270 --> 00:42:27,040
<font color="yellow">What are you doing? Follow him.</font>

640
00:42:28,140 --> 00:42:29,300
<font color="yellow">Why should I?</font>

641
00:42:29,800 --> 00:42:33,140
<font color="yellow">He took me to the hospital and carried me. You'll just let him go?</font>

642
00:42:33,540 --> 00:42:35,700
<font color="yellow">It's dinnertime. You should offer him food.</font>

643
00:42:35,800 --> 00:42:37,040
<font color="yellow">You want me to ask him to stay for food?</font>

644
00:42:37,140 --> 00:42:38,770
<font color="yellow">You made galbitang this morning.</font>

645
00:42:38,770 --> 00:42:40,400
<font color="yellow">Fix a meal with that along with some grilled fish.</font>

646
00:42:40,510 --> 00:42:41,870
<font color="yellow">What is wrong with you?</font>

647
00:42:41,970 --> 00:42:43,840
<font color="yellow">Go catch him before he leaves.</font>

648
00:42:43,840 --> 00:42:45,300
<font color="yellow">Go on. Hurry up!</font>

649
00:42:46,340 --> 00:42:47,670
<font color="yellow">All right. I'm going.</font>

650
00:42:48,100 --> 00:42:49,170
<font color="yellow">Hurry up.</font>

651
00:42:53,070 --> 00:42:54,140
<font color="yellow">Have a seat.</font>

652
00:43:00,870 --> 00:43:03,570
<font color="yellow">- Help yourself. - It's okay. I'll just eat at home.</font>

653
00:43:03,570 --> 00:43:06,300
<font color="yellow">If I let you go without feeding you, Hyo Won, that brat...</font>

654
00:43:06,670 --> 00:43:08,940
<font color="yellow">I mean, my daughter will lose it.</font>

655
00:43:09,570 --> 00:43:10,640
<font color="yellow">No, I mean,</font>

656
00:43:11,540 --> 00:43:13,100
<font color="yellow">she will be very angry at me.</font>

657
00:43:15,170 --> 00:43:16,300
<font color="yellow">Why are you chuckling?</font>

658
00:43:16,740 --> 00:43:19,400
<font color="yellow">I think Ms Min takes after you.</font>

659
00:43:20,170 --> 00:43:21,970
<font color="yellow">That's what people say.</font>

660
00:43:22,340 --> 00:43:25,470
<font color="yellow">I used to be pretty like her when I was young.</font>

661
00:43:25,940 --> 00:43:27,570
<font color="yellow">You're still beautiful.</font>

662
00:43:28,840 --> 00:43:30,540
<font color="yellow">You know how to butter up the elders.</font>

663
00:43:30,770 --> 00:43:31,940
<font color="yellow">I mean it.</font>

664
00:43:33,100 --> 00:43:34,170
<font color="yellow">Eat up.</font>

665
00:43:37,100 --> 00:43:39,170
<font color="yellow">- Aren't you going to eat? - Not now.</font>

666
00:43:39,540 --> 00:43:41,800
<font color="yellow">I'm going to eat with my son when he gets home later.</font>

667
00:43:41,970 --> 00:43:43,400
<font color="yellow">Don't worry about me.</font>

668
00:43:43,770 --> 00:43:45,300
<font color="yellow">Thank you. It looks delicious.</font>

669
00:43:51,740 --> 00:43:54,540
<font color="yellow">To be honest, Hyo Won...</font>

670
00:43:55,870 --> 00:43:58,170
<font color="yellow">is way too much for you to handle.</font>

671
00:43:59,370 --> 00:44:03,540
<font color="yellow">Just being smart isn't enough to get married into a rich family.</font>

672
00:44:03,740 --> 00:44:07,970
<font color="yellow">It's nothing to be proud of, so I don't like to talk about it openly,</font>

673
00:44:09,370 --> 00:44:11,570
<font color="yellow">but people know about it anyway.</font>

674
00:44:12,470 --> 00:44:16,170
<font color="yellow">My older daughter married a guy from a normal family...</font>

675
00:44:16,670 --> 00:44:18,240
<font color="yellow">but ended up getting divorced.</font>

676
00:44:18,940 --> 00:44:22,440
<font color="yellow">Love couldn't conquer the difference in status and class.</font>

677
00:44:23,040 --> 00:44:26,340
<font color="yellow">So I suggest that you come to your senses...</font>

678
00:44:26,570 --> 00:44:28,600
<font color="yellow">and give up on dating Hyo Won.</font>

679
00:44:28,600 --> 00:44:30,740
<font color="yellow">I'm not interested in Ms Min.</font>

680
00:44:32,100 --> 00:44:34,300
<font color="yellow">You're not interested in my daughter? Why not?</font>

681
00:44:34,500 --> 00:44:36,570
<font color="yellow">This may sound rude, but she's not my type.</font>

682
00:44:36,670 --> 00:44:38,770
<font color="yellow">So you have nothing to worry about.</font>

683
00:44:38,970 --> 00:44:40,070
<font color="yellow">My gosh.</font>

684
00:44:40,900 --> 00:44:43,340
<font color="yellow">Well, I'm relieved to hear that.</font>

685
00:44:44,740 --> 00:44:47,240
<font color="yellow">But what's wrong with my daughter? Why is she not your type?</font>

686
00:44:47,470 --> 00:44:48,840
<font color="yellow">From her looks to her academic background,</font>

687
00:44:49,300 --> 00:44:51,540
<font color="yellow">she's certainly an amazing catch.</font>

688
00:44:52,900 --> 00:44:54,340
<font color="yellow">She is,</font>

689
00:44:54,600 --> 00:44:59,170
<font color="yellow">but what you're concerned about will not happen. Please don't worry.</font>

690
00:45:01,370 --> 00:45:02,440
<font color="yellow">All right.</font>

691
00:45:07,000 --> 00:45:09,040
<font color="yellow">He can be quite manly.</font>

692
00:45:10,800 --> 00:45:11,840
<font color="yellow">Shall I fix dinner for you?</font>

693
00:45:11,840 --> 00:45:12,900
<font color="yellow">No, it's okay.</font>

694
00:45:16,400 --> 00:45:17,900
<font color="yellow">Try this, too.</font>

695
00:45:18,770 --> 00:45:20,270
<font color="yellow">- Do we have a guest? - Yes.</font>

696
00:45:20,470 --> 00:45:23,000
<font color="yellow">Some guy carried Hyo Won home.</font>

697
00:45:23,170 --> 00:45:25,270
<font color="yellow">Someone carried her home? Who is the guy?</font>

698
00:45:25,470 --> 00:45:27,670
<font color="yellow">He's having dinner with Madam Ko in the kitchen now.</font>

699
00:45:34,170 --> 00:45:37,270
<font color="yellow">I see. You must like tteokgalbi.</font>

700
00:45:38,370 --> 00:45:40,470
<font color="yellow">Did Hyo Won get a boyfriend?</font>

701
00:45:44,800 --> 00:45:47,140
<font color="yellow">I think he was one of the models at the fashion show.</font>

702
00:45:58,270 --> 00:45:59,640
<font color="yellow">Who's Young Eun?</font>

703
00:45:59,640 --> 00:46:00,740
<font color="yellow">His first love.</font>

704
00:46:00,740 --> 00:46:04,040
<font color="yellow">His what? He had a first love?</font>

705
00:46:04,140 --> 00:46:07,440
<font color="yellow">He brought her to the tailor shop a few times a long time ago...</font>

706
00:46:07,440 --> 00:46:10,270
<font color="yellow">and introduced her to Mr Lee and me.</font>

707
00:46:12,370 --> 00:46:13,840
<font color="yellow">What a liar.</font>

708
00:46:14,540 --> 00:46:18,340
<font color="yellow">He has been lying to me that I'm his first love.</font>

709
00:46:20,500 --> 00:46:24,040
<font color="yellow">What is this smell? Are you going to burn all the chicken?</font>

710
00:46:25,240 --> 00:46:28,340
<font color="yellow">Gosh, I'm sorry. I was distracted.</font>

711
00:46:36,900 --> 00:46:39,440
<font color="yellow">Why are you getting home so late? I'm starving.</font>

712
00:46:39,540 --> 00:46:40,670
<font color="yellow">It's not like I was out playing.</font>

713
00:46:40,770 --> 00:46:42,570
<font color="yellow">- What about dinner? - Just eat this.</font>

714
00:46:43,440 --> 00:46:44,670
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

715
00:46:44,670 --> 00:46:47,900
<font color="yellow">You can't even cook dinner for your husband who worked hard all day?</font>

716
00:46:48,740 --> 00:46:50,170
<font color="yellow">How can you tell me to just eat fried chicken?</font>

717
00:46:50,170 --> 00:46:52,240
<font color="yellow">I also worked hard all day.</font>

718
00:46:52,340 --> 00:46:54,140
<font color="yellow">Fix dinner for yourself if you want something else.</font>

719
00:46:54,240 --> 00:46:55,900
<font color="yellow">Are you really going to be like this?</font>

720
00:46:56,000 --> 00:46:58,540
<font color="yellow">It's up to me to decide whether I'm going to be like this or not.</font>

721
00:46:58,640 --> 00:47:00,470
<font color="yellow">Gosh, I'm so sick of this.</font>

722
00:47:04,800 --> 00:47:06,370
<font color="yellow">Sure, you're sick of me.</font>

723
00:47:06,740 --> 00:47:08,640
<font color="yellow">It's autumn now, so you must also miss your first love.</font>

724
00:47:08,840 --> 00:47:09,970
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

725
00:47:11,500 --> 00:47:12,600
<font color="yellow">That little...</font>

726
00:47:13,270 --> 00:47:16,170
<font color="yellow">- Ms Bok. It's me, Da Jeong. - Yes, come in.</font>

727
00:47:21,440 --> 00:47:23,670
<font color="yellow">Here. This registered mail came for you earlier today,</font>

728
00:47:23,670 --> 00:47:26,100
<font color="yellow">and Grandma signed it for you. She asked me to give it to you.</font>

729
00:47:26,300 --> 00:47:27,700
<font color="yellow">Oh, I see. Thanks.</font>

730
00:47:27,800 --> 00:47:29,000
<font color="yellow">You're welcome. Have a restful evening.</font>

731
00:47:29,100 --> 00:47:30,440
<font color="yellow">All right. Good night.</font>

732
00:47:35,170 --> 00:47:37,940
<font color="yellow">I guess it's from the bank.</font>

733
00:47:39,740 --> 00:47:42,140
<font color="yellow">(Notice of Acceleration)</font>

734
00:47:42,440 --> 00:47:46,170
<font color="yellow">"Notice of Acceleration"?</font>

735
00:47:48,100 --> 00:47:49,340
<font color="yellow">"Certification of contents"?</font>

736
00:47:49,700 --> 00:47:52,300
<font color="yellow">(Total Amount Owed: 56,300 Dollars)</font>

737
00:47:52,300 --> 00:47:53,500
<font color="yellow">What is going on?</font>

738
00:47:58,570 --> 00:48:00,000
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

739
00:48:01,000 --> 00:48:02,140
<font color="yellow">What is this?</font>

740
00:48:05,100 --> 00:48:06,100
<font color="yellow">What's this?</font>

741
00:48:06,100 --> 00:48:08,240
<font color="yellow">Why are you asking me?</font>

742
00:48:08,440 --> 00:48:10,800
<font color="yellow">It looks like you agreed to guarantee someone's debt.</font>

743
00:48:13,040 --> 00:48:17,300
<font color="yellow">This is... I think I agreed to be a guarantor when my friend, Yong Suk,</font>

744
00:48:17,300 --> 00:48:20,100
<font color="yellow">from the orphanage was starting a business about 10 years ago.</font>

745
00:48:22,140 --> 00:48:24,800
<font color="yellow">Just a second. Where's Yong Suk's number?</font>

746
00:48:25,840 --> 00:48:29,770
<font color="yellow">The number you have dialled does not exist. Please check...</font>

747
00:48:29,770 --> 00:48:31,840
<font color="yellow">The number does not exist. What is going on?</font>

748
00:48:31,840 --> 00:48:33,300
<font color="yellow">What did I tell you?</font>

749
00:48:33,640 --> 00:48:36,340
<font color="yellow">I told you that you should never guarantee anyone's debt.</font>

750
00:48:36,340 --> 00:48:38,140
<font color="yellow">Hold on a second. This guy, Yong Suk,</font>

751
00:48:38,140 --> 00:48:40,670
<font color="yellow">would never eat up my money and disappear. I'll try to find him.</font>

752
00:48:40,670 --> 00:48:42,840
<font color="yellow">Come to your senses already.</font>

753
00:48:43,070 --> 00:48:45,670
<font color="yellow">We always had issues when you did this in the past.</font>

754
00:48:45,770 --> 00:48:48,440
<font color="yellow">We always ended up having to clear all the debts.</font>

755
00:48:50,340 --> 00:48:51,870
<font color="yellow">We lost our store,</font>

756
00:48:52,040 --> 00:48:53,770
<font color="yellow">and we're going to lose all of our money now.</font>

757
00:48:54,040 --> 00:48:56,940
<font color="yellow">When will we save enough to buy a home and a car?</font>

758
00:48:56,940 --> 00:48:59,400
<font color="yellow">Will we ever get to live like other people?</font>

759
00:48:59,400 --> 00:49:01,070
<font color="yellow">I'll just pay it off.</font>

760
00:49:01,170 --> 00:49:04,400
<font color="yellow">It's over 50,000 dollars. How will you pay it off?</font>

761
00:49:05,100 --> 00:49:07,700
<font color="yellow">We even got a notice of acceleration. If we can't pay it,</font>

762
00:49:07,700 --> 00:49:09,500
<font color="yellow">there will be seizure tickets all over the place.</font>

763
00:49:09,700 --> 00:49:12,670
<font color="yellow">You'll become a credit delinquent. What are you going to do?</font>

764
00:49:12,870 --> 00:49:15,740
<font color="yellow">That's for me to worry about. Mind your own business.</font>

765
00:49:15,740 --> 00:49:17,170
<font color="yellow">How can you say it like that?</font>

766
00:49:17,670 --> 00:49:20,340
<font color="yellow">- Am I a stranger to you? - I wish you were.</font>

767
00:49:21,040 --> 00:49:23,470
<font color="yellow">- What did you say? - You're always like this.</font>

768
00:49:23,740 --> 00:49:27,040
<font color="yellow">Nothing matters to you besides money and babies, right?</font>

769
00:49:28,240 --> 00:49:29,370
<font color="yellow">Gosh.</font>

770
00:49:34,270 --> 00:49:35,470
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

771
00:49:42,400 --> 00:49:43,440
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

772
00:49:44,240 --> 00:49:47,940
<font color="yellow">Don't craw back in here before you get that money back.</font>

773
00:49:49,300 --> 00:49:51,300
<font color="yellow">- Are you kicking me out right now? - Yes, I am.</font>

774
00:49:52,440 --> 00:49:56,170
<font color="yellow">You should learn a lesson on the value of money.</font>

775
00:50:06,800 --> 00:50:09,370
<font color="yellow">Don't come back until you have that 50,000 dollars.</font>

776
00:50:09,370 --> 00:50:10,370
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

777
00:50:10,570 --> 00:50:14,700
<font color="yellow">I won't come back even if you beg, so don't worry.</font>

778
00:50:15,770 --> 00:50:18,500
<font color="yellow">You should run back to your first love, Young Eun.</font>

779
00:50:18,500 --> 00:50:19,570
<font color="yellow">Young Eun?</font>

780
00:50:20,600 --> 00:50:21,940
<font color="yellow">How do you know Young Eun?</font>

781
00:50:22,140 --> 00:50:23,470
<font color="yellow">You horrible man.</font>

782
00:50:23,940 --> 00:50:25,640
<font color="yellow">Get out of my face!</font>

783
00:50:26,040 --> 00:50:27,670
<font color="yellow">What's going on out there?</font>

784
00:50:31,000 --> 00:50:32,370
<font color="yellow">What's that suitcase for?</font>

785
00:50:32,740 --> 00:50:35,270
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry for making a fuss, Mr Lee and Ms Choi.</font>

786
00:50:40,170 --> 00:50:42,670
<font color="yellow">Where is Sam Do going?</font>

787
00:50:43,100 --> 00:50:44,370
<font color="yellow">I kicked him out.</font>

788
00:50:44,570 --> 00:50:45,640
<font color="yellow">- You did what? - What?</font>

789
00:50:45,740 --> 00:50:48,170
<font color="yellow">He guaranteed someone's debt without telling me again.</font>

790
00:50:48,600 --> 00:50:50,270
<font color="yellow">We received a letter of demand from the bank.</font>

791
00:50:50,370 --> 00:50:52,170
<font color="yellow">- What? - I'm sick of it.</font>

792
00:50:52,170 --> 00:50:54,400
<font color="yellow">I'm done cleaning up after his mess.</font>

793
00:50:54,840 --> 00:50:56,400
<font color="yellow">I can't do it any more.</font>

794
00:50:56,670 --> 00:50:58,140
<font color="yellow">I've had enough.</font>

795
00:50:58,270 --> 00:51:01,970
<font color="yellow">But still, how can you kick him out at this time of the night?</font>

796
00:51:02,070 --> 00:51:05,170
<font color="yellow">He'll figure it out on his own. I'll go back upstairs.</font>

797
00:51:10,740 --> 00:51:14,970
<font color="yellow">First it's you, and now it's Sam Do.</font>

798
00:51:15,270 --> 00:51:17,070
<font color="yellow">What should we do about him?</font>

799
00:51:17,570 --> 00:51:18,740
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

800
00:51:20,700 --> 00:51:26,170
<font color="yellow">You said that I should leave you first</font>

801
00:51:26,500 --> 00:51:33,370
<font color="yellow">You said you only wanted me to see your pretty moments</font>

802
00:51:33,640 --> 00:51:39,740
<font color="yellow">You told me to leave you there</font>

803
00:51:40,000 --> 00:51:42,300
<font color="yellow">- Susanna - Stop right there.</font>

804
00:51:43,900 --> 00:51:46,540
<font color="yellow">- But this is the good part. - It's an opening ceremony.</font>

805
00:51:46,670 --> 00:51:50,000
<font color="yellow">You'll scare off every customer if you sing such a sad song.</font>

806
00:51:50,170 --> 00:51:52,470
<font color="yellow">We don't want you to sing a sad song.</font>

807
00:51:52,670 --> 00:51:54,900
<font color="yellow">Can't you sing anything cheerful? A trot song, perhaps?</font>

808
00:51:55,770 --> 00:51:56,940
<font color="yellow">Trot?</font>

809
00:51:59,400 --> 00:52:00,870
<font color="yellow">But I'm a rock ballad singer.</font>

810
00:52:01,070 --> 00:52:04,870
<font color="yellow">What? Who sings rock at a cabaret?</font>

811
00:52:05,100 --> 00:52:08,170
<font color="yellow">- The song needs to be exciting. - Come on.</font>

812
00:52:08,870 --> 00:52:11,570
<font color="yellow">- Sing us some trot songs. - What?</font>

813
00:52:14,540 --> 00:52:16,670
<font color="yellow">I think you've got the wrong person.</font>

814
00:52:17,000 --> 00:52:19,800
<font color="yellow">I don't sing trot songs. I'm a rocker.</font>

815
00:52:20,140 --> 00:52:21,440
<font color="yellow">- A rocker. - Hey, come on.</font>

816
00:52:21,440 --> 00:52:24,270
<font color="yellow">They really want to hear you sing.</font>

817
00:52:24,570 --> 00:52:26,170
<font color="yellow">Come on and sing us a trot song.</font>

818
00:52:26,600 --> 00:52:29,340
<font color="yellow">I'll pass. No matter how desperate I may be,</font>

819
00:52:29,570 --> 00:52:31,740
<font color="yellow">I can't just throw away my rock spirit.</font>

820
00:52:32,640 --> 00:52:33,700
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

821
00:52:34,300 --> 00:52:35,370
<font color="yellow">Jun.</font>

822
00:52:36,500 --> 00:52:38,300
<font color="yellow">- Jun. - Don't come out.</font>

823
00:52:38,870 --> 00:52:39,870
<font color="yellow">Come on.</font>

824
00:52:48,100 --> 00:52:49,440
<font color="yellow">Dong Sook.</font>

825
00:52:50,570 --> 00:52:52,770
<font color="yellow">- Get in. - Are we...</font>

826
00:52:53,170 --> 00:52:55,640
<font color="yellow">going to eat at that diner again?</font>

827
00:52:57,770 --> 00:52:59,540
<font color="yellow">I can't take you to the same place again.</font>

828
00:52:59,740 --> 00:53:02,070
<font color="yellow">Today, I'll be giving you a tour around the two buildings...</font>

829
00:53:02,240 --> 00:53:03,570
<font color="yellow">I own in Jongno.</font>

830
00:53:03,770 --> 00:53:08,170
<font color="yellow">After that, we'll go to Gwangjang Market, and I'll buy you...</font>

831
00:53:08,170 --> 00:53:09,470
<font color="yellow">bindaetteok and gimbap.</font>

832
00:53:10,070 --> 00:53:12,670
<font color="yellow">Bindaetteok and gimbap?</font>

833
00:53:12,900 --> 00:53:14,940
<font color="yellow">Are they not to your liking?</font>

834
00:53:15,240 --> 00:53:18,400
<font color="yellow">They're quite popular at the market.</font>

835
00:53:18,770 --> 00:53:21,470
<font color="yellow">Fine. I know a nice snack bar next to that place.</font>

