846
00:54:02,270 --> 00:54:04,370
<font color="yellow">Dong Sook is getting what she deserves.</font>

847
00:54:06,970 --> 00:54:10,900
<font color="yellow">When will I ever get a car like that and give Dong Sook a ride?</font>

848
00:54:21,870 --> 00:54:23,440
<font color="yellow">- Excuse me. - Yes?</font>

849
00:54:23,570 --> 00:54:25,270
<font color="yellow">Can we turn on the heater?</font>

850
00:54:25,470 --> 00:54:27,170
