863
00:55:03,370 --> 00:55:04,600
<font color="yellow">You're ridiculous.</font>

864
00:55:05,370 --> 00:55:08,440
<font color="yellow">Why bother driving a car, then? You could just walk.</font>

865
00:55:09,500 --> 00:55:12,000
<font color="yellow">I love a woman who thinks like that.</font>

