875
00:56:11,900 --> 00:56:13,240
<font color="yellow">I came to see you.</font>

876
00:56:13,770 --> 00:56:15,770
<font color="yellow">That's not what's important right now.</font>

877
00:56:16,340 --> 00:56:18,870
