878
00:56:19,440 --> 00:56:20,500
<font color="yellow">Let's go.</font>

879
00:56:22,040 --> 00:56:23,300
<font color="yellow">Here you go.</font>

880
00:56:25,800 --> 00:56:28,940
<font color="yellow">Do you know what kind of position you put me in?</font>

