884
00:56:38,900 --> 00:56:40,800
<font color="yellow">and made a fool of myself.</font>

885
00:56:41,800 --> 00:56:43,500
<font color="yellow">You asked him that directly?</font>

886
00:56:44,400 --> 00:56:46,940
<font color="yellow">- Yes. - How could you do that?</font>

887
00:56:46,940 --> 00:56:48,070
<font color="yellow">He must've been embarrassed.</font>

888
00:56:48,300 --> 00:56:51,340
<font color="yellow">It wasn't like that. He got really upset.</font>

889
00:56:51,700 --> 00:56:54,140
<font color="yellow">He looked at me like I was some crazy woman.</font>

