00:56:55,800 --> 00:56:57,270
<font color="yellow">Of course it is.</font>

892
00:56:57,800 --> 00:57:01,370
<font color="yellow">He didn't even make eye contact with me today.</font>

893
00:57:01,470 --> 00:57:04,240
<font color="yellow">Why did you ask him that, anyway?</font>

894
00:57:05,470 --> 00:57:09,000
<font color="yellow">I was worried that he actually might have a crush on me.</font>

895
00:57:09,300 --> 00:57:10,840
<font color="yellow">Why would you be worried?</font>

896
00:57:10,940 --> 00:57:13,000
<font color="yellow">Someone like him shouldn't...</font>

897
00:57:14,140 --> 00:57:16,170
<font color="yellow">Well, I know it's not possible,</font>

898
00:57:16,800 --> 00:57:19,400
<font color="yellow">but if he does actually like me,</font>

899
00:57:19,740 --> 00:57:20,770
<font color="yellow">that would be terrible.</font>

900
00:57:20,870 --> 00:57:22,400
<font color="yellow">How is that terrible?</font>

901
00:57:22,600 --> 00:57:25,770
<font color="yellow">I'm not well educated nor do I have a wealthy background.</font>

902
00:57:26,400 --> 00:57:28,470
<font color="yellow">I also have Gi Pyo.</font>

903
00:57:28,470 --> 00:57:32,100
<font color="yellow">Technically speaking, you and him have nothing going on.</font>

904
00:57:32,440 --> 00:57:35,170
<font color="yellow">You have every right to see someone you like.</font>

905
00:57:35,600 --> 00:57:37,270
<font color="yellow">Don't think you're not a match for Dong Jin.</font>

906
00:57:37,470 --> 00:57:39,600
<font color="yellow">Stop saying things like that.</font>

907
00:57:39,800 --> 00:57:43,140
<font color="yellow">You made things get awkward between me and him.</font>

908
00:57:43,600 --> 00:57:46,400
<font color="yellow">He thinks I'm silly a woman.</font>

909
00:58:01,270 --> 00:58:03,540
<font color="yellow">I guess she decided to go home right away.</font>

910
00:58:05,270 --> 00:58:06,300
<font color="yellow">Dong Jin.</font>

911
00:58:07,100 --> 00:58:08,470
<font color="yellow">What brings you here?</font>

912
00:58:08,900 --> 00:58:11,070
<font color="yellow">I stopped by when I saw the lights on.</font>

913
00:58:11,070 --> 00:58:12,640
<font color="yellow">You did? Take a seat.</font>

914
00:58:16,700 --> 00:58:19,870
