00:58:28,340 --> 00:58:29,870
<font color="yellow">I told her something I shouldn't have.</font>

918
00:58:30,170 --> 00:58:32,370
<font color="yellow">It's my fault, not hers. Please go easy on her.</font>

919
00:58:32,800 --> 00:58:33,900
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

920
00:58:34,000 --> 00:58:36,470
<font color="yellow">To be honest, I'm the one who told her that...</font>

921
00:58:36,470 --> 00:58:39,140
<font color="yellow">you might have a crush on her.</font>

922
00:58:40,700 --> 00:58:43,900
<font color="yellow">Why would you think that?</font>

