00:58:58,170 --> 00:59:01,170
<font color="yellow">It's true that I have good feelings for her.</font>

928
00:59:02,400 --> 00:59:06,240
<font color="yellow">But I'm not sure if those feelings are what you said they could be.</font>

929
00:59:06,800 --> 00:59:08,570
<font color="yellow">She's a good person.</font>

930
00:59:09,070 --> 00:59:12,800
<font color="yellow">But I think it's more like a feeling of sympathy...</font>

931
00:59:13,000 --> 00:59:15,670
<font color="yellow">for everything she's going through.</font>

932
00:59:15,870 --> 00:59:17,800
<font color="yellow">That's not what it looked like to me.</font>

933
00:59:18,870 --> 00:59:22,270
<font color="yellow">To be honest, I don't know what I'm feeling right now.</font>

934
00:59:22,740 --> 00:59:24,640
<font color="yellow">I'm trying to ask myself that.</font>

935
00:59:24,940 --> 00:59:29,470
<font color="yellow">So until I do find an answer, don't tell Yun Shil about it.</font>

936
00:59:29,700 --> 00:59:30,940
<font color="yellow">Can you keep the promise?</font>

937
00:59:31,370 --> 00:59:34,740
<font color="yellow">She already has enough worries. I don't want to bother her.</font>

938
00:59:35,300 --> 00:59:37,000
<font color="yellow">I understand.</font>

939
00:59:39,600 --> 00:59:41,840
<font color="yellow">Sam Do. What's all that?</font>

