00:59:55,840 --> 00:59:59,870
<font color="yellow">The two of you should join forces at times of hardship.</font>

946
01:00:00,040 --> 01:00:02,870
<font color="yellow">This is the third time...</font>

947
01:00:03,170 --> 01:00:04,770
<font color="yellow">he threw away money for guaranteeing someone's debt.</font>

948
01:00:04,940 --> 01:00:07,040
<font color="yellow">It'd be easier to make a cow understand...</font>

949
01:00:07,470 --> 01:00:09,140
<font color="yellow">than to get through to him.</font>

950
01:00:09,140 --> 01:00:11,570
<font color="yellow">I understand why you're upset,</font>

951
01:00:11,870 --> 01:00:16,500
<font color="yellow">but he might get really angry and never come back.</font>

952
01:00:16,940 --> 01:00:18,540
<font color="yellow">I don't care.</font>

953
01:00:20,500 --> 01:00:23,240
<font color="yellow">I have to get some sleep. Please take Ms Choi and leave.</font>

954
01:00:36,700 --> 01:00:39,040
<font color="yellow">He always gets used by other people.</font>

955
01:00:39,670 --> 01:00:42,870
<font color="yellow">I have to teach him a lesson once and for all.</font>

956
01:00:46,670 --> 01:00:48,270
<font color="yellow">Oh, my head.</font>

957
01:00:56,970 --> 01:01:01,100
<font color="yellow">I was just worried as a co-worker. That's why I treated you like that.</font>

958
01:01:01,700 --> 01:01:05,140
<font color="yellow">I guess my acts of kindness made you get the wrong idea.</font>

959
01:01:05,940 --> 01:01:07,740
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry for giving you the wrong impression.</font>

960
01:01:08,240 --> 01:01:09,570
<font color="yellow">I'll be careful from now on.</font>

961
01:01:13,740 --> 01:01:16,700
<font color="yellow">Why am I crying? Silly me.</font>

962
01:01:49,440 --> 01:01:50,770
<font color="yellow">Is that you, Yun Shil?</font>

963
01:01:51,140 --> 01:01:53,570
<font color="yellow">You didn't have breakfast yet, right?</font>

964
01:01:53,840 --> 01:01:57,140
<font color="yellow">Mum made seaweed soup for your birthday today.</font>

965
01:01:57,570 --> 01:02:00,270
<font color="yellow">You should come over before you go to work.</font>

966
01:02:00,470 --> 01:02:02,240
<font color="yellow">Don't refuse.</font>

967
01:02:02,570 --> 01:02:06,600
<font color="yellow">Mum made it just for you, so stop by for some, okay?</font>

968
01:02:07,170 --> 01:02:08,500
<font color="yellow">Okay. I'll see you later.</font>

969
01:02:09,870 --> 01:02:12,170
<font color="yellow">Is it Yun Shil's birthday today?</font>

970
01:02:12,170 --> 01:02:16,000
<font color="yellow">Yes. Mum made seaweed soup and breakfast for her.</font>

971
01:02:16,170 --> 01:02:19,170
<font color="yellow">Mum didn't want to leave her all alone on her birthday.</font>

972
01:02:19,300 --> 01:02:20,370
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

973
01:02:39,340 --> 01:02:40,900
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

974
01:02:41,600 --> 01:02:42,600
<font color="yellow">Hi.</font>

975
01:02:43,300 --> 01:02:47,970
<font color="yellow">Ms Choi asked me to come and have some seaweed soup.</font>

976
01:02:48,270 --> 01:02:51,100
<font color="yellow">I heard that it's your birthday today.</font>

