01:03:17,140 --> 01:03:18,370
<font color="yellow">What are you trying to say?</font>

983
01:03:18,470 --> 01:03:21,600
<font color="yellow">I know you're baffled and upset...</font>

984
01:03:21,800 --> 01:03:24,170
<font color="yellow">because of what I said to you,</font>

985
01:03:26,140 --> 01:03:29,600
<font color="yellow">but how can you change your attitude completely overnight?</font>

986
01:03:32,470 --> 01:03:34,370
<font color="yellow">Does it hurt your pride that much...</font>

987
01:03:34,800 --> 01:03:36,870
<font color="yellow">to be mistaken for...</font>

988
01:03:37,470 --> 01:03:39,770
<font color="yellow">having a crush on me?</font>

989
01:03:41,240 --> 01:03:43,700
<font color="yellow">- It's not like that. - Why did you buy me those shoes?</font>

990
01:03:44,270 --> 01:03:46,600
<font color="yellow">Why did you follow me to the temple?</font>

991
01:03:46,700 --> 01:03:49,840
<font color="yellow">Why did you bring me medicine and porridge when I was sick?</font>

992
01:03:49,840 --> 01:03:52,340
<font color="yellow">Why did you fix my sink?</font>

993
01:03:53,570 --> 01:03:55,900
<font color="yellow">Why did you walk me home,</font>

994
01:03:56,700 --> 01:03:59,400
<font color="yellow">worry about me and say nice things to me?</font>

995
01:04:01,840 --> 01:04:03,100
<font color="yellow">It's...</font>

996
01:04:04,170 --> 01:04:08,100
<font color="yellow">I'm trying to figure out why I did all those things.</font>

