01:04:08,170 --> 01:04:12,240
<font color="yellow">You can hurt people's feelings with unintended kindness.</font>

998
01:04:13,370 --> 01:04:14,600
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

999
01:04:14,700 --> 01:04:17,540
<font color="yellow">You're a well-educated and well-off man,</font>

1000
01:04:18,000 --> 01:04:22,840
<font color="yellow">so I guess you took pity in me because I looked pathetic to you.</font>

1001
01:04:24,100 --> 01:04:27,900
<font color="yellow">But you can't blame me for getting the wrong impression.</font>

1002
01:04:28,100 --> 01:04:29,340
<font color="yellow">It's not like that.</font>

1003
01:04:29,440 --> 01:04:30,470
<font color="yellow">To be honest,</font>

1004
01:04:32,170 --> 01:04:33,340
<font color="yellow">I'm relieved.</font>

1005
01:04:34,370 --> 01:04:36,170
<font color="yellow">About what?</font>

1006
01:04:36,170 --> 01:04:39,770
<font color="yellow">I'm relieved that someone like you doesn't have interest in me.</font>

1007
01:04:41,040 --> 01:04:44,600
<font color="yellow">Do you know how worried I was in case you actually did like me?</font>

1008
01:04:44,700 --> 01:04:46,000
<font color="yellow">Is me liking you...</font>

1009
01:04:46,900 --> 01:04:48,400
<font color="yellow">a worrying matter?</font>

1010
01:04:50,270 --> 01:04:53,240
<font color="yellow">It's a good thing for someone to like someone else.</font>

1011
01:04:53,700 --> 01:04:55,400
<font color="yellow">Why do you have to be worried?</font>

1012
01:04:55,670 --> 01:04:58,700
<font color="yellow">It's my fault for getting the wrong idea,</font>

1013
01:04:59,100 --> 01:05:02,300
<font color="yellow">but you're also responsible for giving the wrong impression.</font>

1014
01:05:03,100 --> 01:05:05,700
<font color="yellow">Let's call it even.</font>

1015
01:05:08,670 --> 01:05:11,240
<font color="yellow">That's all what I wanted to say.</font>

1016
01:05:12,770 --> 01:05:15,640
<font color="yellow">I'll get going now.</font>

1017
01:05:23,470 --> 01:05:27,240
<font color="yellow">Do you have any idea how confused I am with myself?</font>

1018
01:05:28,940 --> 01:05:30,370
<font color="yellow">Call it even, my foot.</font>

1019
01:05:44,170 --> 01:05:47,400
<font color="yellow">We agreed on each other's faults.</font>

1020
01:05:48,100 --> 01:05:49,770
<font color="yellow">This is a done deal.</font>

