01:06:27,870 --> 01:06:30,370
<font color="yellow">(The Gentlemen of Wolgyesu Tailor Shop)</font>

1022
01:06:30,970 --> 01:06:33,170
<font color="yellow">Watch yourself. Just because the goalkeeper is missing...</font>

1023
01:06:33,170 --> 01:06:34,800
<font color="yellow">doesn't mean you can play around with the ball.</font>

1024
01:06:34,800 --> 01:06:36,040
