1025
01:06:36,140 --> 01:06:38,240
<font color="yellow">How low do you have to get to like someone like her?</font>

1026
01:06:38,340 --> 01:06:40,470
<font color="yellow">Is this the best you can do? Do you know how much damage...</font>

1027
01:06:40,470 --> 01:06:42,170
<font color="yellow">you caused to my company?</font>

1028
01:06:42,170 --> 01:06:44,800
<font color="yellow">What happened? Is this because of the 30,000 dollars?</font>

1029
01:06:44,900 --> 01:06:46,000
<font color="yellow">What's this, Mr Lee?</font>

1030
01:06:46,000 --> 01:06:48,540
<font color="yellow">This won't be enough, but it'll help.</font>

1031
01:06:48,540 --> 01:06:50,670
<font color="yellow">Everyone makes mistakes.</font>

1032
01:06:50,670 --> 01:06:53,440
<font color="yellow">My acts of kindness weren't out of sympathy or pity.</font>

1033
01:06:53,440 --> 01:06:56,040
<font color="yellow">I gave it a lot of thought. and I think I...</font>

